*genkernel-3.0.1_beta12 (14 Feb 2004)

  14 Feb 2004; Brad House <brad_mssw@gentoo.org> genkernel-3.0.1_beta1.ebuild,
  genkernel-3.0.1_beta12.ebuild, genkernel-3.0.1_beta2.ebuild,
